ntralisation by a return to the pattern of dispersal that was the norm in earlier years, then this sensitivity test would be of less rele</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">vance.</span></h3><h3 style="font-size:11pt; font-weight:normal; line-height:113%; margin:10pt 0pt 0pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">1.3.6</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">Note this </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">proposed </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">sensitivity test </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">of the imp</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">a</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">ct of densification </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">is different in nature from th</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">e </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">London Scenario </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">sensitivity test</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">presented o</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">n page 26 of “</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.