<span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">impacts of densification tre</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">nds on reducing car traffic demand per capita within </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">the </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">many other large dense cities across England, nor </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">does it take account </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">of th</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">e </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">substantial </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">reduction in car travel </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">impact</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt"> on the SRN that would </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">result</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">from a greater proportion of the </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">total English </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">p</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:11pt; letter-spacing:0.25pt">opulation being resident </span><span style="font